lyrics:
Kan zain i harh ang u,
Rilru leh thlarauvin;
Kan Lalpa rawngbawl hna hi,
Lawm taka thawk zelin;
Hneh hnuah kanlawmman tur,
A tiam kha hre rengin;
Lawmna lui a lo luang ang,
Kan Pa duhzawng tihin.

Krista leh Kohhran,
Kan engkim kan hlan e;
Krista leh Kohhran,
Kan dam chhan ber ni se.

Kan zain i bei ang u,
Khawvel sual hneh turin;
Khawiah pawh sual zinga mi,
Thlarau chhandam turin;
Chanchin Tha hi hril zelin,
Khawvel tawp thleng pawhin;
Thihna daihlima thuten,
Chu ri chu an hria ang.

Kan zain i thawk ang u,
Krista Kohhran tan hian;
Rinawm taka thawk zelin,
Kan engkim pawh phalin;
A dan tinreng zawm zellin,
A thil serh ngaisangin;
Chutin Krista ang tur
in,
Dam chhung kan sang zel ang.
